    HIChartsJSONSerializable

    public class HIPareto
extends HISeries
    A pareto series. If the type option is not specified, it is inherited from chart.type. For options that apply to multiple series, it is recommended to add them to the plotOptions.series options structure. To apply to all series of this specific type, apply it to [plotOptions. pareto](#plotOptions.pareto).
